[AssaultRifle_LS X2WeaponTemplate]
FriendlyName="Laser Rifle"
FriendlyNamePlural="Laser Rifles"
BriefSummary="The Laser Rifle emits a series of microsecond-duration blasts of light that destroy chemical bonds in targets."
TacticalText="<Bullet/> Firing the primary weapon ends the soldier's turn, in the absence of special training.\n<Bullet/> Use upgrades recovered from ADVENT enemies to improve the laser rifles's tactical effectiveness.\n<Bullet/> The high-energy output of these laser weapons is derived from integrating alien technology into discovered pre-war laser weaponry.\n<Bullet/> Laser weapons receive bonus aim."
AbilityDescName="assault rifle"

[SMG_LS X2WeaponTemplate]
FriendlyName="Laser Stengun"
FriendlyNamePlural="Laser Stenguns"
BriefSummary="A lightweight version of the Laser Rifle, this fills a similar role to the SMG, trading power, ammo and accuracy at range for increased soldier mobility and concealment."
; LWOTC Needs Translation
TacticalText="<Bullet/> Firing the primary weapon always ends the soldier's turn, in the absence of special training.\n<Bullet/> Use upgrades recovered from ADVENT enemies to improve the Stengun's tactical effectiveness. \n<Bullet/> SMG-style weapons offer bonus mobility, close-quarters accuracy and concealment relative to assault rifles, but they do less damage and suffer accuracy penalties at long range.\n<Bullet/> Laser weapons receive bonus aim."
; End Translation
AbilityDescName="SMG"

[Cannon_LS X2WeaponTemplate]
FriendlyName="Laser Cannon"
FriendlyNamePlural="Laser Cannons"
BriefSummary="Laser weapons tech combined with an improved cooling system will let us deploy a rapid-fire version of the cannon, able to lay down a much deadlier volume of fire."
TacticalText="<Bullet/> The Laser Cannon is a much more powerful, yet equally deployable, version of the conventional Cannon.\n<Bullet/> Use upgrades looted from enemies to improve the Laser Cannon's tactical effectiveness.\n<Bullet/> Laser weapons receive bonus aim."
AbilityDescName="cannon"

[Shotgun_LS X2WeaponTemplate]
FriendlyName="Scatterray"
FriendlyNamePlural="Scatterray"
BriefSummary="The Scatterray is an application of laser technology to provide shotgun-like effects; it is most effective at close range due to beam diffusion."
TacticalText="<Bullet/> Shotgun-style weapons are extremely effective at close range, but their accuracy drops off quickly at longer range.\n<Bullet/> Use upgrades looted from enemies to improve the Scatterray's tactical effectiveness.\n<Bullet/> Laser weapons receive bonus aim."
AbilityDescName="shotgun"

[SniperRifle_LS X2WeaponTemplate]
FriendlyName="Laser Lance"
FriendlyNamePlural="Laser Lances"
BriefSummary="A long rifle version of the Laser Rifle, the Laser Lance incorporates extremely high-energy flash capacitors, resulting in a high-precision long-range laser weapon."
TacticalText="Sniper rifles always require both actions to fire.\n<Bullet/> They are less accurate at close range, but deadly at a distance.\n<Bullet/> Use upgrades looted from enemies to improve the Laser Lance's tactical effectiveness.\n<Bullet/> Laser weapons receive bonus aim."
AbilityDescName="sniper rifle"
